.TH Lang_files
.SH NAME
\[char46]lang \- files with translation data
.SH DESCRIPTION
.b Lang files
Lang files are using same format as configuration files.
.br
\[char46]lang files could have any name, they need to be placed in
lang directories in order to be loaded by engine.
.br
.SH EXAMPLE
In order to translate, for example, item name and info, we need to add following
line to one of module \[char46]lang files:
.nf
itemID:name;info
.SH SEE ALSO
config
dirs/lang